              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "DIFFR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A neutron interferometer splits the neutron",
                "matter wave into two paths using Bragg diffraction in",
                "single Si crystal. On one path a sample is placed.",
                "After the sample, two beams are reflected and",
                "recombined, which produce interference that is",
                "observable by neutron counters located behind the",
                "crystal."
              ]
            }
